Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 880
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Shell "bash"
Set Framerate 15
Set WindowBar "Colorful"

Hide
Type "cd /tmp"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "calibrcv --help"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3500ms

Type "calibrcv score resume.pdf"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 7s
